ffects like extended range are so rare? At least for int casters that is. To my knowledge outside of any potime goodies only 2 items have druzzil's distance for casters the staff from air, and the earring from rallos zek, while priests can use the earring and the necklace from pofire, and the bracer from poearth, and probably something I'm forgetting. Even the caster bracer from earth doesn't have druzzil's distance like the others! Wouldn't it be nice if some of the existing mana preservation effects were changed to more usefule effects like druzzil distance, general damage focus, or the like? <p>Silvius Wayfarer<br>
65th Arcanist of Drinal<br>
< Cats in Hats ><br>
<A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=249725">
<IMG SRC="http://members.cox.net/tremere3/pie.gif"><br>My Stuff </A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zealpath00>ZealPath00</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br>  Posts: 618<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/7/03 2:56 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Unbalanced Spell Focus Effects!</span><hr size=1> Yeah that would be nice, although there is one more Druzzil's Distance item wizards can use, <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_item_info.html?num=20896">Air Fetish</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> off Avatar of Wind.<br>
<br>
All things considered it would be nice if some existing mana preservation effects (I have 3 myself), especially the one on Xegony Vest were something else... I mean anyone likely to get a Xegony Vest is probably going to have elemental sleeves with the same preservation, among possible other things like a conservation of solusek item (which for wizards is nearly the same as preservation of xegony, etc).<br>
<br>
As far as what effect to change it too, well range is a good one since we don't exactly have a vast selection there. Another couple Anger of Solusek items probably wouldn't hurt either, only 2 around that I know of atm. <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=7124" TARGET="_blank">Sage Zealpath Skyphire</A><BR>
